Name: BrowseDrive
Version: 2.2
Summary: UNKNOWN
Home-page: UNKNOWN
License: UNKNOWN
Description: BrowseDrive is a package that allows for one to download the browser driver files used during browser automation with selenium. This package covers downloads for geckodriver and chromedriver. This package also has a module for the automation of browser drivers. 
        
        ## Installation
        ```python
        pip3 install BrowseDrive==2.1
        
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        ```python 
        import BrowseDrive
        from BrowseDrive.driverdownloader import DriverDownloader
        
        ```
        
        ## Downloading drivers 
        ```python
        downloader = DriverDownloader() 
        downloader.set_savepath("") # Save path goes inside here
        downloader.download() # Starts the download process
        
        ```
        
        
